Objects.name: Kenny
Objects.Talkable: I heard that the path to Destiny lies in the top right corner of Faith!::Is there any more information you can give me?:1@@There are some portals hidden in the center!

Objects.name: GreyWarden
Objects.Talkable: I love 308 so much I want to take it again.

Objects.Questable: Item Quest;;getdestiny;;1061906850;;Go forth and look for your destiny!
Objects.name: Amy
Objects.Talkable: Welcome to Duke!::What am I supposed to do?:1@@To find your destiny in life, you will need to travel through the various areas of Duke to look for this Destiny! Go forth and find your major and destiny::Can you give me a clue?:2@@I am feeling gracious and shall give you a clue. There are many areas of Duke, including Envy, Sloth, Faith, Grasslands of Despair and finallly Destiny::Mhm:3@@You are looking for Destiny but in order to get through them, you will need to go through the other areas of Duke to get clues of how to get there. It can get confusing because there are invisible teleporting portals everywhere!::Where are the portals on this map!:4@@Well there are 4 portals on this map, leading to the different rooms. If I'm not wrong, they are on the 4 corners of the map!
